<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.10">
<l>kuṇṭai vayiṟṟuk kuṟiya ciṟiya neṭiya piṟaṅkaṟpē</l>
<l>yiṇṭu paṭarnta viruḷcūḻ mayāṉat terivā yeyiṟṟuppēy</l>
<l>koṇṭu kuḻavi taṭavi veruṭṭik koḷḷeṉ ṟicaipāṭa</l>
<l>miṇṭi miḷirnta caṭaikaḷ tāḻa vimala ṉāṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As short, small, long, tall demonesses with hollow bellies</l>
<l>on the burial ground surrounded by darkness that is spread with acacias,</l>
<l>with demonesses with teeth in flame mouths grope for [their] children in fright, while [they] sing noisily,</l>
<l>while [his] full twisted matted locks hang down the Spotless one is dancing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
